ygData.subject: Reminder for new members
ygData.msgSnippet: Just letting new members know that if your messages aren t going through right away it is because they have to be approved by a moderator before they can be
ygData.messageBody:
Just letting new members know that if your messages aren't going through
right away it is because they have to be approved by a moderator before they
can be posted.
I don't like having to do this, but it became necessary due to high volumes
of spam.
I need to fix the intro message to say this though. I'll have to remember to
do it later.
luv,
-Su (list owner)
